<br>
As for a confrontation that never existed, I can only assume you are a recent newcomer to EQ.  The three elements of VerantSpeak that I promulgated over a year ago as a sardonic commentary on Verant's approach at the time struck home because there WAS a bit of truth behind each one.<br>
